message.body: Cuuuuutie!!!
Hi baby, what's up?
Nufin... I'm in ocean gate so I'm gonna leave for work from here in the morning, what's up with u?
Word I don't wanna be at work at 7 :( lol
My hardworking cutie! Not much here....finished up my work for the night, probably hitting it early because I have to catch a train tomorrow AM....blah
But at least your week ends after tomorrow!!
But I just want to sleeeeeeeep
Come here and sleep with me, I'm in such a mood to cuddle with you right now
.....YOU TELL ME THIS NOW!?
I didn't know I was getting it to myself =p so when can u get here? Lol
Unfortunately I'm an hour and a half away, and we both have early mornings =P
Laaaaaame
I have to go to rehearsal after work :(
Now THAT is lame...
Tell me about it...... Le sigh
So when do I get to see my sweetie?
Whenever I don't have rehearsal or work =p
Well yeah, is that ever? Lolz
I'm free Wednesday's completely =p
Hmm.....Wednesdays are a sucky day for me, insofar as I get in from tutoring around 7 (soon to be like 8).....
IDEA lets both quit everything and just live on the beach forever
Now that would be the best thing ever wouldn't it =p I'm going to sleep, good night baby, I love you, sleep tight, sweet dreams, we'll plan something out soon
Goodnight sweetie, I love you too, sweet dreams! Let's shoot for Wednesday, we'll figure something out and see each other so soon
Just realized I'll be out of training on Wednesday by 12pm - wanna do something after that?
Yes I do :)
Whee! Where will you be based? I'll be coming from way north in Summit, but I'm sure I can secure the car
I'll be in Middletown
Probably not unfortunately =p
Aww man, haha. No matter, I'm just happy to be with you =)
I love spendin time with my cutie :)
Wanna see a movie? Theatre is only 40 minutes from Summit
Hazlet theater?
Yup yup
Ok, what movie do u wanna see?
Man of Steel, Star Trek, Now You See Me, Oz? I would see any of them. I'm also super behind on movies =P
Let's see now u see me :)
Let's do that then
There's a 1:40!
Okey. =) If only we hadn't lost our parking lot spot
I know right.... We could always just check again =p
This is true
The struggle is real...
My God, but we do have problems, don't we? Haha
Hardly, it's a young couple thing
Trolololol
No security but people come and go
Isn't tomorrow supposed to be raining anyway? Lol
Well yes, but what does that have to do with anything? =P
Right today is Monday, nvm lol
What would happen if it was raining? Haha
No one would be in the park...... Because its raining =p
Seems to only be raining tomorrow, seems to only be cloudy on Wednesday
Yes they do, I've seen them in grimm's office
Ooh! Thanks for the heads up. Let's not do that then....
It's okay really, I'm just very happy I get you to myself on Wednesday =)
I love being with my cutie :)
Me too, you're the cutest and nicest and sweetest and most handsome and most wonderful man I know =)
Ur the best thing that happened to me :)
And you're the best thing that happened to me! I don't know what I would do without you =)
Sleep is a great thing :) lol
You finally got the sleep you deserve! Haha. What are you up to today?
Just rehearsal later tonight, doing things with tech tonight =p hbu?
Fun stuff, I'm about to go into a psych study - making BANK this summer
Look at u, being all psychological =p
....the experimenter got mixed up, I already did this study, but got $10 for the 15 minutes I had actually done....haha. Heading home now, I guess...
Awe haha was it worth it? Lol
I was there anyway, I don't mind any. Now I have time to do my GRE and psych homework =P
Yay!! Got ur work done!!
But I don't wanna do work, I just want to eat and sleep =P
Well I can't argue with that feeling =p
Such is life. =P Hey, wanna get lunch tomorrow before or after the movie?
Yeah that sounds great :)
Okay! Does before or after work better for you?
Hmmmmmmmm...... Doesn't matter to me really =p
It depends on if you want to sleep in =P
I think we should eat prior and then that'll be my breakfast and then we can do whatever =p
Sounds good to me =P
12:45ish at Bertucci's? That'll give us enough time
When's the movie?
Yeah that should be plenty of time :)
Yay! I'm excited to see you =)
I love seein my cutie :)
You know what today would be great for? Snuggling with my cutie
This is a fantastic day for snuggling, come and snuggle with me!!!
But but but you have practice
Come after!!! Lol
But but I have orientation early in the morning!!
Laaaaaaaane
I can't wait to not have class any more, then we can at least have Mondays together =P
Yay!!! But I have work on Monday's.... Lol
Monday nights =P
Yay monday nights!!!
I just realized! Our 2 year is on a Monday, so we can see each other!'
I misread that for a second and thought u said it was this Monday lol but that's exciting!!
On *a* Monday, lolz. I remember it cause it was the day after the last Harry Potter came out....
That was last year or two years ago? Lol
Two years ago!
Yeah not a die hard Harry potter so I didnt make that connection =p
Shannon's party is the easier connection =P
Yeah thats what I remember =p
You were so cute that night!
U were the cute one, I vommitted =p
Somehow the nervousness was endearing =P
BLLLLAAAAAAAAAAARRRRRRRGH
Would you have still asked me out if I had left after you vomited? Lolz
That's an interesting question, hmmmmm...... May have taken me a little longer to do so but I think I would have
I'm very happy I stayed, regardless =P
Me too, it would have been a much odder situation had u not =p
Yyyyeaaaaahhh....I would not have known how to proceed, haha
